    <data key="d0">Extreme Reach Adbridge Video Distribution Architecture</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5EmA67lSJEs</data>
    <data key="d2">System processes and transcodes major US advertising traffic, using SQS queues for asynchronous task prioritization and S3 for direct-to-destination delivery.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, compute_intensive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
  </graph>
